979	
980	The processor consumes `raw_event` jobs from the `github` BullMQ queue. Each job has shape `{ event: string; installationId: number; payload: unknown; receivedAt: Date }`.
981	
982	For each event type it:
983	1. Looks up the installation DB record by `installationId`
984	2. Looks up the repo by `github_repo_id` from the payload
985	3. Upserts contributor(s) involved
986	4. Upserts the relevant entity (commit/PR/review/review_comment)
987	5. Handles `installation_repositories` to sync repos
